========,2,Popular culture.
The 2001 film "Brigham City" was actually filmed in Mapleton, instead of the film's namesake, Brigham City, Utah.
The 2011 TV movie, A Christmas Wish, was filmed and set in Mapleton.
The 2016 movie, The Christmas Project, was filmed in Mapleton.
